{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"8a9ec5ba6e","title":"与教堂订立的协定","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"54d3c7098f","index":0,"year":1936,"month":12,"day":28,"articleId":"8a9ec5ba6e"}],"tags":[{"id":"523bb79e8f","name":"周恩来","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji9-2","name":"毛泽东全集第9卷(2)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji9-2.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji9-2":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"ab1cab1c80","type":"paragraph","text":"与教堂订立的协定！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"8a9ec5ba6e"},{"id":"fc9cc4f2b5","type":"paragraph","text":"1936年12月28日）","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"8a9ec5ba6e"},{"id":"49896f43c0","type":"paragraph","text":"（甲）教堂承认苏维埃红军之抗日救国及反军阀卖国贼之主张，苏维埃红军承认教堂之存在。（乙）拒绝一切国民党军阀之军队、民团、侦探进入教堂区域，一切教民均为苏维埃公民，服从苏维埃法律，苏维埃红军承认宣教与信教的自由。（丙）教堂之财产不没收，由教堂自动捐助抗日救国经费。（丁）经济通商不加阻碍。（戊）其他事项随时协商办理","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"8a9ec5ba6e"},{"id":"7bddc984d9","type":"paragraph","text":"[1]为争取教堂与苏维埃红军建立和平友好关系，毛泽东和周恩来联名提出与各教堂订立协定。这是毛泽东和周恩来提出的协定的主要内容。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"8a9ec5ba6e"}],"page":{"id":"6400a743e5","publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"8a9ec5ba6e","start":228,"end":228}}}},"__N_SSG":true}